      • setOpacity

        public void setOpacity(boolean opacity)
        Switches the opacity state of the image. This forces the SquareProgressBar to redraw with the current progress. As bigger the progress is, then more of the image comes to view. If the progress is 0, then you can't see the image at all. If the progress is 100, the image is shown full.
        选择透明度状态。这迫使进度条重绘。进度越大图片显示出来越多。
        参数:
        opacity - true if opacity should be enabled.
        从以下版本开始:
        1.2.0

      • setOpacity

        public void setOpacity(boolean opacity,
                       boolean isFadingOnProgress)
        Switches the opacity state of the image. This forces the SquareProgressBar to redraw with the current progress. As bigger the progress is, then more of the image comes to view. If the progress is 0, then you can't see the image at all. If the progress is 100, the image is shown full.
        选择透明度状态。这迫使进度条重绘。进度越大图片透明度越低。 You can also set the flag if the fading should get inverted so the image disappears when the progress increases.
        你也可以设置flag，如果透明度的变化需要跟进度条相反，这样的话进度条越大图片透明度越高
        参数:
        opacity - true if opacity should be enabled.
        isFadingOnProgress - default false. This changes the behavior the opacity works. If the progress increases then the images fades. When the progress reaches 100, then the image disappears.
        从以下版本开始:
        1.4.0

      • setImageGrayscale

        public void setImageGrayscale(boolean greyscale)
        You can set the image to b/w with this method. Works fine with the opacity.

        greyscale - true if the grayscale should be activated.
